%% Data Flow Diagram - ilab-on-ocp
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant DSPA as Data Science Pipelines<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prereqs as Prerequisites Check Pod
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Git as Git Repository<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SDGPod as SDG Pod
    participant Teacher as Teacher Model (Mixtral)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PVC as Shared PVC (/data, /model)
    participant DataProc as Data Processing Pod
    participant Launcher as Training Launcher Pod
    participant Master as PyTorchJob Master<br/>MASTER_PORT/TCP
    participant Workers as PyTorchJob Workers
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPUs
    participant MTBench as MT-Bench Eval Pod
    participant Judge as Judge Model (Prometheus)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM (localhost)<br/>dynamic/TCP
    participant FinalEval as Final Eval Pod
    participant UploadPod as Upload Model Pod
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS

    User->>DSPA: Submit pipeline run<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    DSPA->>Prereqs: Launch prerequisites task

    Note over Prereqs,K8sAPI: Phase 1: Prerequisites Validation
    Prereqs->>K8sAPI: Check Training Operator, DSPA, Model Registry<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    Prereqs->>Teacher: Validate teacher endpoint<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (api_token)
    Prereqs->>Judge: Validate judge endpoint<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (api_token)

    Note over SDGPod,PVC: Phase 2: Synthetic Data Generation
    SDGPod->>Git: Clone taxonomy repo<br/>Auth: Basic-auth or SSH key
    SDGPod->>Teacher: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Teacher-->>SDGPod: Completion responses
    SDGPod->>PVC: Write generated data to /data

    Note over DataProc,PVC: Phase 3: Data Processing
    DataProc->>PVC: Read SDG data, process for training
    DataProc->>PVC: Write processed training data

    Note over Launcher,GPU: Phase 4: Distributed Training
    Launcher->>K8sAPI: Create PyTorchJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Launcher: PyTorchJob created
    Master->>PVC: Load training data & base model
    Master->>Workers: Rendezvous (NCCL/Gloo)<br/>plaintext TCP
    Master->>GPU: CUDA/NCCL compute
    Workers->>GPU: CUDA/NCCL compute
    Master->>PVC: Save trained model checkpoint
    Launcher->>K8sAPI: Monitor PyTorchJob status

    Note over MTBench,vLLM: Phase 5: MT-Bench Evaluation
    MTBench->>PVC: Load trained model
    MTBench->>vLLM: Start local vLLM server
    MTBench->>vLLM: GET /v1/models (health check)
    MTBench->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions
    vLLM-->>MTBench: Model responses
    MTBench->>Judge: POST /v1/chat/completions (judging)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Judge-->>MTBench: Judge scores

    Note over FinalEval,vLLM: Phase 6: Final Evaluation (MMLU + MT-Bench-Branch)
    FinalEval->>PVC: Load candidate & base models
    FinalEval->>vLLM: Serve models locally
    FinalEval->>Judge: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Judge-->>FinalEval: Comparative scores

    Note over UploadPod,MR: Phase 7: Model Upload & Registration
    UploadPod->>PVC: Read trained model
    UploadPod->>OCI: Push ModelCar image (skopeo)<br/>Auth: Docker auth (.dockerconfigjson)
    UploadPod->>MR: Register model version<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
